tour-de-grid.title: Tour de Grid Ride Tracker
tour-de-grid.runInfo: Join us on Sat., Sept 9th for a 9-mile ride from Wicker Park through West Town, Garfield Park, and Humboldt Park. Hop on a Bike Bus from Lincoln Square, Bridgeport, Hyde Park, or Austin to get there!

stops.name: Central Park Dr. and Schraeder Dr.

taste-the-grid-north.title: Taste of the Grid Ride Tracker
taste-the-grid-north.runInfo: Join us this Sunday as we explore what riding a bike in Chicago could be like on The Grid. We'll be riding (~10mph) this loop twice, so feel free to hang out at the Glenwood Sunday Market from 9:55-11AM, we'll be back to pick you up.
